Diarrhea is one of the side effects of antibiotics.

 Antibiotic associated diarrhea can be encountered between two hours to two months after starting of antibiotics.

 The purpose of the study is to determine incidence,risk factors and severity of pediatric antibiotic associated diarrhea in Turkey.

